        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"William Kelley\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n William Kelley:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>That\u2019s nice to hear! I love these wines. We did a vertical with Chiara, Emidio\u2019s granddaughter, a few weeks ago back to 1983. Of the young wines, the 2001 and 2010 really stood out. Clearly I need to source some of the 2011 too\u2026</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>I buy the MdA every year.  Producer vastly outweighs vintage when it comes to Pepe.</p>",
